This work is based on Llama3.1-70B. 
We also ran Stage 1 studies using other LLMs.
With a 10x smaller Llama-8B model, recall fell below 50% (compared to ca. 80% with the 70B model).
With GPT-3.5, preliminary experiments showed results similar to Llama-70B. 
Still, a broader comparison of different LLMs for our task would be desirable.